Package: publicholidays
Type: Package
Title: Wrap Nager.Date API and provide valuable holiday insights for various business applications.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Huan He, Qijia Zheng
Maintainer: Huan He <raccoonhe@gmail.com>, Qijia Zheng <zqj1999@gmail.com>
Description: 
    The "publicholidays" package is designed to simplify the process of accessing Nager.Date API and retrieve detailed holiday information for over 100 countries. By leveraging the API's robust capabilities, this package allows users to gain valuable holiday insights for various business applications.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Imports: 
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    tibble
